title: Shopnotes issues 71 - 80 - Good Quality
description:
These are the best I could find.

#80 has a smallish file size & is not as clear as the others but actually looks ok.
#76, 77 & 78 &#039;open small&#039; but when magnified 2-3 times to fill the page look very good. The file size / resolution reflect this.

What I mean is, all are scanned nicely, really clear. 
They open and scroll well - some I came accross didn&#039;t. 
They open to fill the full window of Acrobat or Foxit - others didn&#039;t.

They are all full issues - they are not articles/sections taken from various issues.
